15,01thunder and lightning
15,01the spark and the moan
15,01Cas mother earth and
15,01father sky
15,01reach for a kiss
15,01rising from her body
15,01to his lips
15,01the echos shake our bones
15,01of a passion so great
15,01it once shaped mountains
15,01and gods and men...
15,01 
15,01reaching for the sky...
15,01Our love lifts up 
15,01to a flash so bright
15,01it can't be sustained
15,01 
15,01bowed to the earth
15,01Our hearts know
15,01that something like this
15,01can't be explained...
15,01 
